  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The roller shutter and housing box is unacceptable in terms of design, appearance and location. It&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;would fail to preserve the character and appearance of the host building and conservation area&lt;/span&gt;.  &lt;/span&gt;As such, the development is contrary to policies LP1 (&amp;nbsp;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-ce19ff34-7fff-81fb-1a84-e4e53ac1fa50&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Design quality and local character&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, LP3 (&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Designated heritage assets). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;SPG, &#x27;Shop front design guide&#x27;. Policies &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;D4 (Delivering good design ), HC1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 12pt; font-family: FoundryFormSans-Bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Heritage conservation and growth) of the London Plan. &amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
